Erin Daniels https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erin_Daniels 0 Erin Daniels (born October 9, 1973) is an American actress. She is best known for her role as Dana Fairbanks on The L Word (2004–2007). Her feature film work includes A Single Man and One Hour Photo. Erin_Daniels ( born October_9_,_1973 ) is an_American_actress .
